| File | Change |
| ------ | -------- |
| `.github/workflows/comprehensive-tests.yml` | Replaced matrix strategy with single sequential job (22 steps) |
| `justfile` | Added `-debug-level=line-tables` to mojo invocations in `_test-group-inner` recipe |

